Relevant key strokes:
    up/down arrows - navigate past inputs
    escape - clear current input
    return - enter your current input

Normal accepted inputs:
    inventory
    eat (food)
    move/go (compass direction)
    health
    drop (item)
    give (item)
    look
    clear/cls
    help

Differences between difficulties:
    Max number of turns to win in
    Hard difficulty doesn't get told coordinates
    How often you are attacked when north of the wall

Known issues/things to do/suggestions:
    trying to give away an item where it shouldn't be currently says "i don't know what you mean." change?
    something should signify losing/winning other than just saying you've won/lost
    add more differences between difficulties
    add conversations
    eventually add health/inventory to the html page
    multiple items pickup?